{"tid":2203824,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"梁定邦拒正面回應警7.21「新真相」 望市民信法律：唔信法庭就乜都冇得信","createTime":"2020-09-15T14:59:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-16T01:57:19.000Z","uid":240362,"like":3,"dislike":73,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"abb0563dc35fcc483d0b845ec8a9f5eeb2e25f82","tid":2203824,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T14:59:59.000Z","msg":"警方早前就元朗7.21事件以暴動罪拘捕多人，新界北總區刑事總部高級警司陳天柱交代案件時，將當晚情況重新演繹，包括形容為兩派人士的衝突、雙方「勢均力敵、旗鼓相當」，說法引起全城譁然。監警會主席梁定邦今午（15日）回應時，拒絕正面回應警方所描繪的「新真相」，認為事件目前應交由法庭處理，又多次強調社會應相信法律制度。<br />\n<br />\n梁亦多次強調社會必須要相信法律制度，認為「如果你唔信法庭，就乜嘢都冇得信」，又指自己對事件的看法沒有討論意義，「我有啲咩意見冇咩意思」。<br />\n<br />\n特首林鄭月娥在監警會報發表同日見記者時，以「香港的真相」作為演講佈景板，有記者質疑如監警會報告是「香港的真相」，陳天柱的說法會否不尊重報告、甚至重寫新真相。梁定邦回應時稱，有關形容僅屬林鄭的做法，「請你問一問問特首，呢啲唔係我嘅說話」，又強調報告內容基於事實及援引紀錄，表示他「唔會隨便講一句說話」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200915/DSHTBH2GI5AL3JZBJILVO7Z22A/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200915%2FDSHTBH2GI5AL3JZBJILVO7Z22A%2F&d=ulKCtXgG4rwmRR8qyGKIuRZZVu6JdVYNpUv5YkkCXtQ%3D&h=ff7d3c08\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200915%2FDSHTBH2GI5AL3JZBJILVO7Z22A%2F&h=24872095\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200915/DSHTBH2GI5AL3JZBJILVO7Z22A/</a>"},{"pid":"b5a562845318cd712cf84d5b95a6594c34f17ce9","tid":2203824,"uid":133,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T15:00:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05a71dd567a42ce1a7e95493d606cc9b633beedd","tid":2203824,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T15:01:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ki